1
00:00:15,640 --> 00:00:16,480
Forget it.

2
00:00:17,710 --> 00:00:18,800
I won't wear it.

3
00:00:19,390 --> 00:00:20,030
Yes.

4
00:00:22,870 --> 00:00:24,390
What he remembers

5
00:00:25,160 --> 00:00:27,620
should be what I looked like
with black hair.

6
00:00:29,180 --> 00:00:31,750
Back then, I rarely wore hairpins.

7
00:00:32,750 --> 00:00:34,210
I thought they were tacky.

8
00:00:35,150 --> 00:00:35,940
Mi,

9
00:00:37,370 --> 00:00:38,860
am I really getting old?

10
00:00:41,110 --> 00:00:44,370
Do you think Shaoying will be disappointed
when he sees me?

11
00:00:44,750 --> 00:00:46,560
You are not old at all, Your Majesty.

12
00:00:46,560 --> 00:00:47,710
You are just as beautiful

13
00:00:47,710 --> 00:00:50,440
as when you sent
Young Master Shaoying off to war.

14
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:55,750
Never mind.

15
00:00:57,470 --> 00:00:58,470
I'll put it on.

16
00:01:02,110 --> 00:01:03,640
It can cover up my gray hair.

17
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:06,300
This will be our last meeting.

18
00:01:07,070 --> 00:01:09,320
I hope he'll remember me at my best.

19
00:01:10,950 --> 00:01:12,010
Yes, Your Majesty.

20
00:01:31,860 --> 00:01:33,940
Your Majesty, maybe we shouldn't go.

21
00:01:34,340 --> 00:01:37,870
You've been in so much pain
that you haven't slept well for days.

22
00:01:39,530 --> 00:01:40,979
I want to go and hear

23
00:01:42,060 --> 00:01:43,620
what the other life

24
00:01:44,580 --> 00:01:46,780
that little girl talked about was like.

25
00:01:49,979 --> 00:01:50,910
-Let's go.
-Yes.

26
00:02:04,340 --> 00:02:05,870
What is the meaning of this?

27
00:02:06,090 --> 00:02:07,060
The Eagle King has ordered

28
00:02:07,060 --> 00:02:09,460
us to protect the Empress Dowager tonight.

29
00:02:09,460 --> 00:02:10,259
Your Majesty,

30
00:02:10,570 --> 00:02:12,460
could His Highness already know

31
00:02:12,570 --> 00:02:14,700
that you are meeting Mr. Yuan tonight?

32
00:02:18,900 --> 00:02:20,220
We are here under the Eagle King's orders.

33
00:02:20,220 --> 00:02:22,530
Tonight, the Jiankang Palace
is welcoming Princess Pingning.

34
00:02:22,530 --> 00:02:24,060
Fearing that Southern Ye
might cause trouble,

35
00:02:24,060 --> 00:02:25,340
we were specifically ordered
to protect you.

36
00:02:25,340 --> 00:02:27,600
I am the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin.

37
00:02:27,620 --> 00:02:30,480
Do my words
carry less weight than the Eagle King's?

38
00:02:30,570 --> 00:02:31,460
Step aside!

39
00:02:33,460 --> 00:02:34,970
Are you trying to rebel?

40
00:02:35,060 --> 00:02:35,850
Hold on!

41
00:02:43,740 --> 00:02:44,900
Xie Huaigui?

42
00:02:46,410 --> 00:02:47,810
This is a state affair of Northern Qin.

43
00:02:47,810 --> 00:02:49,090
We will not tolerate outsiders
interfering.

44
00:02:49,090 --> 00:02:51,690
Please conduct yourself with dignity,
My Lord.

45
00:02:51,690 --> 00:02:53,940
You are now on the territory of Ye.

46
00:02:53,940 --> 00:02:56,070
Naturally, you must abide by our laws.

47
00:02:56,340 --> 00:02:59,620
Besides, the Empress Dowager
is an old friend of mine.

48
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:02,250
I wish to invite her
for a chat today.

49
00:03:03,340 --> 00:03:05,780
And as the Grand Tutor of Ye,

50
00:03:06,410 --> 00:03:08,900
would I plot against the Empress Dowager?

51
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:14,300
Please, Your Majesty.

52
00:04:42,159 --> 00:04:46,280
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

53
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:49,270
[Episode 13]

54
00:04:52,500 --> 00:04:55,740
Grand Tutor, you didn't
break into Honglu Temple tonight

55
00:04:56,540 --> 00:04:57,810
just to get me

56
00:04:58,690 --> 00:05:00,250
out of this, did you?

57
00:05:01,330 --> 00:05:04,010
Is Hongyan Pavilion
in the Capital still there?

58
00:05:05,300 --> 00:05:06,810
It has now been renamed

59
00:05:08,010 --> 00:05:09,060
Lishui Pavilion.

60
00:05:10,250 --> 00:05:12,620
Twenty-five years ago,
the An and Lu families

61
00:05:12,620 --> 00:05:15,060
were executed at Hongyan Pavilion.

62
00:05:15,660 --> 00:05:16,860
You still can't let go

63
00:05:18,010 --> 00:05:20,010
of that ill-fated past, can you?

64
00:05:22,450 --> 00:05:23,660
Isn't what you're doing tonight

65
00:05:23,660 --> 00:05:25,010
also to put an end to that

66
00:05:25,010 --> 00:05:26,870
ill-fated past from 25 years ago?

67
00:05:28,540 --> 00:05:29,500
Everyone knows that back then,

68
00:05:29,500 --> 00:05:32,409
you and the youngest son of
the Right King of Virtue of Northern Qin,

69
00:05:32,409 --> 00:05:34,270
Mulian Ying, were deeply in love.

70
00:05:34,620 --> 00:05:37,180
But you were forced to marry into
the Northern Qin royal court.

71
00:05:37,180 --> 00:05:38,980
The Right King of Virtue
amassed military power and acted independently.

72
00:05:38,980 --> 00:05:42,240
He bribed the An and Lu families of Ye
with generous rewards

73
00:05:42,620 --> 00:05:46,210
and colluded with their armies
to fabricate military achievements.

74
00:05:46,210 --> 00:05:47,810
When the scheme was exposed,

75
00:05:48,659 --> 00:05:50,590
all these families were wiped out.

76
00:05:51,330 --> 00:05:54,890
The tragedy of the past is still vivid

77
00:05:55,770 --> 00:05:57,890
in my mind.

78
00:05:59,940 --> 00:06:03,660
I just want one word of truth from you.

79
00:06:05,010 --> 00:06:07,500
The case of the An and Lu families
back then—

80
00:06:09,810 --> 00:06:11,180
were they innocent?

81
00:06:12,250 --> 00:06:13,980
You're unwilling to accept it.

82
00:06:14,690 --> 00:06:16,060
I can understand.

83
00:06:17,210 --> 00:06:20,420
But back then, the An and Lu clans

84
00:06:20,860 --> 00:06:24,060
did collude with
our Right King of Virtue of Northern Qin.

85
00:06:24,890 --> 00:06:26,550
The evidence is irrefutable,

86
00:06:27,250 --> 00:06:28,710
and there was no frame-up.

87
00:06:34,740 --> 00:06:35,800
Stop the carriage!

88
00:06:37,890 --> 00:06:38,940
Grand Tutor Xie,

89
00:06:39,540 --> 00:06:41,400
we are both in our twilight years.

90
00:06:41,500 --> 00:06:44,360
The past should be left behind
like a flowing river.

91
00:06:45,250 --> 00:06:46,510
Those who should let go

92
00:06:47,100 --> 00:06:48,300
should let go.

93
00:07:00,770 --> 00:07:01,370
Master.

94
00:07:09,300 --> 00:07:11,370
Yaoyao asked me to tell you tonight

95
00:07:12,030 --> 00:07:15,210
that you must get the Empress Dowager
safely to Xiyue Restaurant.

96
00:07:15,210 --> 00:07:16,500
Now, only she

97
00:07:16,810 --> 00:07:18,250
can help you keep Lejun.

98
00:07:18,790 --> 00:07:20,990
[Xiyue Restaurant]

99
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:27,270
[Closed]

100
00:07:36,620 --> 00:07:37,890
My Lady, bad news.

101
00:07:38,060 --> 00:07:40,330
The Eagle King has put
the entire Honglu Temple on high alert.

102
00:07:40,330 --> 00:07:41,790
No one is allowed in or out.

103
00:07:42,130 --> 00:07:45,260
Could the Eagle King
already know about tonight's plan?

104
00:07:47,250 --> 00:07:48,780
The Eagle King is ruthless.

105
00:07:49,330 --> 00:07:50,180
Once he's cornered,

106
00:07:50,180 --> 00:07:51,780
there's nothing he won't do.

107
00:07:52,010 --> 00:07:53,770
Especially since tonight's plan

108
00:07:53,770 --> 00:07:55,170
will ruin his grand plan.

109
00:07:56,180 --> 00:07:56,740
No.

110
00:07:56,890 --> 00:07:58,150
Shao Yang is in danger.

111
00:07:58,810 --> 00:07:59,810
I must go save her.

112
00:08:24,590 --> 00:08:28,010
♪ A dying memory glimmers low ♪

113
00:08:28,310 --> 00:08:31,990
♪ You appear, but I can't hold you so ♪

114
00:08:32,100 --> 00:08:36,460
♪ Time itself comes to a sudden halt ♪

115
00:08:36,820 --> 00:08:39,520
♪ So desolate ♪

116
00:08:40,100 --> 00:08:43,760
♪ I traded obsession for this loss ♪

117
00:08:43,789 --> 00:08:47,330
♪ If I could lay my heart bare and cross ♪

118
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:52,850
♪ Would you once more have pity on me ♪

119
00:09:07,330 --> 00:09:07,940
Yaoyao.

120
00:09:08,380 --> 00:09:09,090
Mao.

121
00:09:10,140 --> 00:09:11,940
Why did you bring
the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin here?

122
00:09:11,940 --> 00:09:13,270
Did something go wrong?

123
00:09:14,940 --> 00:09:16,300
The auspicious hour has arrived.

124
00:09:16,300 --> 00:09:18,690
Please, Your Highness the Eagle King
and Princess Pingning,

125
00:09:18,690 --> 00:09:20,350
perform the ceremonial bows.

126
00:09:25,300 --> 00:09:27,210
Eagle King, please bow.

127
00:09:30,210 --> 00:09:32,020
Princess Pingning, please bow.

128
00:09:38,260 --> 00:09:40,380
Princess Pingning, please bow.

129
00:09:49,850 --> 00:09:50,570
Hold on!

130
00:09:56,810 --> 00:09:58,810
At the risk of my life,

131
00:09:59,060 --> 00:10:00,920
I oppose the political marriage!

132
00:10:02,260 --> 00:10:03,390
Here is my memorial.

133
00:10:03,850 --> 00:10:05,650
Please review it, Your Majesty!

134
00:10:10,330 --> 00:10:13,610
♪ Mother won't marry off her daughter ♪

135
00:10:13,610 --> 00:10:17,780
♪ The daughter is longing for her love ♪

136
00:10:20,180 --> 00:10:21,850
Step after step, I journey on;

137
00:10:22,610 --> 00:10:24,540
through a thousand miles of snow,
I return.

138
00:10:24,540 --> 00:10:26,540
We haven't seen each other in years.

139
00:10:26,920 --> 00:10:30,000
Shaoying, you've gone gray.

140
00:10:30,940 --> 00:10:32,490
I'm nearly fifty.

141
00:10:33,180 --> 00:10:35,900
Gray hair is hardly surprising.

142
00:10:44,210 --> 00:10:47,260
If you had made it back
on the day I was married,

143
00:10:48,090 --> 00:10:49,550
and we'd left together...

144
00:10:50,900 --> 00:10:53,350
how do you think things
would've turned out?

145
00:10:53,350 --> 00:10:54,140
Shao Yang...

146
00:11:00,330 --> 00:11:01,300
No one's...

147
00:11:03,210 --> 00:11:05,140
called me that in a very long time.

148
00:11:06,660 --> 00:11:07,380
Shao Yang.

149
00:11:09,210 --> 00:11:12,090
Back then, was it you

150
00:11:12,730 --> 00:11:14,730
who suggested that the late Emperor

151
00:11:17,140 --> 00:11:18,400
have my father killed?

152
00:11:47,060 --> 00:11:48,190
Is this cup of tea...

153
00:11:51,090 --> 00:11:52,970
poisoned too?

154
00:12:05,490 --> 00:12:07,950
Perhaps
the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin

155
00:12:08,020 --> 00:12:09,260
had her own reasons.

156
00:12:13,140 --> 00:12:15,090
Mao, if it were you,

157
00:12:15,900 --> 00:12:18,900
would you still want to see
this person you once loved?

158
00:12:25,330 --> 00:12:26,180
How...

159
00:12:27,570 --> 00:12:28,430
has Lejun been?

160
00:12:29,060 --> 00:12:30,020
Tonight is the night the Eagle King

161
00:12:30,020 --> 00:12:31,260
comes to wed Lejun.

162
00:12:31,970 --> 00:12:33,330
Aren't you going to see her off?

163
00:12:33,330 --> 00:12:34,690
I won't let Lejun leave.

164
00:12:34,810 --> 00:12:37,450
So you went to Cui Mansion?

165
00:12:38,900 --> 00:12:41,060
You asked Chief Clerk Cui
to contact the noble families

166
00:12:41,060 --> 00:12:43,660
to help Lejun reject the marriage,
didn't you?

167
00:12:47,020 --> 00:12:48,020
The foundation of Ye

168
00:12:48,020 --> 00:12:49,940
relies on the descendants
of the noble families.

169
00:12:49,940 --> 00:12:52,670
If we send Princess Pingning
to Northern Qin now—

170
00:12:52,780 --> 00:12:54,660
those Northern Qin people
are from a barbaric land.

171
00:12:54,660 --> 00:12:55,450
They are uncivilized

172
00:12:55,450 --> 00:12:56,570
and lack proper etiquette.

173
00:12:56,570 --> 00:12:58,450
Making a noble lady marry a barbarian

174
00:12:58,450 --> 00:13:00,330
is an insult to all noble families.

175
00:13:00,330 --> 00:13:02,610
Your Majesty,
have you forgotten the incident of Wenxi?

176
00:13:02,610 --> 00:13:05,180
In the past, the late Emperor
reduced the lands of the nobles,

177
00:13:05,180 --> 00:13:07,980
and internal strife
plunged the realm into chaos.

178
00:13:08,210 --> 00:13:09,490
Your Majesty, Empress Dowager,

179
00:13:09,490 --> 00:13:11,090
you must not repeat the same mistakes!

180
00:13:11,090 --> 00:13:14,330
Your Majesty, Empress Dowager,
we beg you to reconsider!

181
00:13:17,450 --> 00:13:19,250
Your Majesty, Empress Dowager.

182
00:13:19,490 --> 00:13:21,300
I do not want to marry into Northern Qin,

183
00:13:21,300 --> 00:13:23,020
nor do I want to disgrace Ye's prestige.

184
00:13:23,020 --> 00:13:25,900
I beg you to retract the order!

185
00:13:27,180 --> 00:13:28,940
If the political marriage fails today,

186
00:13:28,940 --> 00:13:30,540
the alliance will be voided.

187
00:13:30,900 --> 00:13:34,160
And the three prefectures
will return to our Northern Qin.

188
00:13:40,540 --> 00:13:42,450
In this puppet show,

189
00:13:44,020 --> 00:13:46,020
do none of us get a good ending?

190
00:13:48,090 --> 00:13:49,220
Jiayu doesn't know—

191
00:13:50,540 --> 00:13:51,940
you didn't want to see me.

192
00:13:56,300 --> 00:13:57,500
You wanted to kill me.

193
00:14:00,140 --> 00:14:01,140
I just want to know

194
00:14:03,100 --> 00:14:04,900
if you have let go of your hatred—

195
00:14:08,850 --> 00:14:10,210
your hatred for my son

196
00:14:11,420 --> 00:14:13,350
and the Northern Qin royal family.

197
00:14:16,900 --> 00:14:17,690
I have.

198
00:14:22,330 --> 00:14:23,210
You are lying.

199
00:14:25,420 --> 00:14:26,820
If you had truly let it go,

200
00:14:27,140 --> 00:14:30,200
why would you forge weapons
under Xiao Wuyi's command?

201
00:14:31,570 --> 00:14:34,540
All these years,
you've been helping the Beifu Army.

202
00:14:34,540 --> 00:14:36,070
You have hated us all along.

203
00:14:36,900 --> 00:14:39,420
You hate me, my son,

204
00:14:39,690 --> 00:14:41,380
and everyone in Northern Qin.

205
00:14:41,660 --> 00:14:43,060
If you had the chance
to overthrow Northern Qin,

206
00:14:43,060 --> 00:14:44,860
you wouldn't miss it, would you?

207
00:14:52,330 --> 00:14:53,060
So...

208
00:14:55,570 --> 00:14:56,940
before I die,

209
00:14:59,140 --> 00:15:00,900
I have to kill you.

210
00:15:07,690 --> 00:15:08,850
If I die,

211
00:15:10,450 --> 00:15:11,910
will you truly be at peace?

212
00:15:20,970 --> 00:15:21,690
Yes.

213
00:15:25,330 --> 00:15:25,970
Alright.

214
00:15:26,540 --> 00:15:27,330
My life...

215
00:15:30,420 --> 00:15:31,150
is yours now.

216
00:15:40,380 --> 00:15:42,020
Young Lord Xiao has arrived!

217
00:15:43,090 --> 00:15:44,420
Young Lord Xiao is here?

218
00:15:45,570 --> 00:15:46,610
Why is he here?

219
00:15:56,380 --> 00:15:57,240
Your Highness.

220
00:15:57,900 --> 00:16:00,700
This is an everlasting Ruyi lantern
I made myself.

221
00:16:01,940 --> 00:16:05,140
I'm presenting it to you
as a  celebration of your wedding.

222
00:16:08,180 --> 00:16:11,140
Greetings, Your Majesty, Empress Dowager.

223
00:16:12,210 --> 00:16:14,660
Since you came to congratulate,

224
00:16:15,300 --> 00:16:16,900
why did you wait until the auspicious hour

225
00:16:16,900 --> 00:16:18,760
almost passed to finally show up?

226
00:16:19,780 --> 00:16:20,660
Tonight

227
00:16:20,660 --> 00:16:23,140
is the wedding of the Eagle King
and Princess Pingning.

228
00:16:23,140 --> 00:16:25,420
All the people of Jiankang
lit lanterns to pray.

229
00:16:25,420 --> 00:16:26,850
Though it made my carriage
difficult to move,

230
00:16:26,850 --> 00:16:28,710
it shows the hearts of the people.

231
00:16:28,850 --> 00:16:31,210
Ye and Northern Qin have formed
an alliance through a political marriage,

232
00:16:31,210 --> 00:16:33,450
ceasing war, nourishing the people,
and reopening trade markets.

233
00:16:33,450 --> 00:16:35,490
There will be no more soldiers
shedding blood.

234
00:16:35,490 --> 00:16:39,210
This is truly a blessing
for all the people.

235
00:16:40,940 --> 00:16:42,600
You are wrong, Your Highness.

236
00:16:43,380 --> 00:16:45,940
Our noble families
have a century-old heritage.

237
00:16:45,940 --> 00:16:47,780
We are the pillars of Ye

238
00:16:47,780 --> 00:16:49,660
and the orthodox lineage of the world.

239
00:16:49,660 --> 00:16:51,090
Now, to form an alliance,

240
00:16:51,450 --> 00:16:52,850
we actually resorted
to a political marriage,

241
00:16:52,850 --> 00:16:55,380
groveling and flattering,
disgracing our national ethos.

242
00:16:55,380 --> 00:16:55,780
We absolutely cannot...

243
00:16:55,780 --> 00:16:56,580
Your Majesty.

244
00:16:57,450 --> 00:16:59,690
I also have a memorial to present today.

245
00:17:00,060 --> 00:17:00,810
Present it.

246
00:17:02,300 --> 00:17:04,230
During the severe flood last year,

247
00:17:05,660 --> 00:17:08,380
the Cui family, the Lu family of Fanyang,

248
00:17:08,380 --> 00:17:09,980
and the Wen family of Qinghe,

249
00:17:10,380 --> 00:17:12,290
under the guise of praying for the people,

250
00:17:12,290 --> 00:17:14,020
held a winding stream banquet.

251
00:17:14,180 --> 00:17:14,859
In reality,

252
00:17:15,490 --> 00:17:17,660
they took the opportunity
to seize the people's land.

253
00:17:17,660 --> 00:17:18,290
May I ask—

254
00:17:20,490 --> 00:17:23,250
is the dignity of the noble families
Chief Clerk Cui spoke of

255
00:17:23,250 --> 00:17:24,579
referring to this?

256
00:17:40,690 --> 00:17:41,580
Now,

257
00:17:42,290 --> 00:17:43,490
can you rest assured?

258
00:17:47,900 --> 00:17:48,820
Why?

259
00:17:49,690 --> 00:17:50,820
After so many years,

260
00:17:51,380 --> 00:17:52,940
don't you hate me?

261
00:17:53,770 --> 00:17:56,140
I know you were the one
who advised the late Emperor

262
00:17:56,140 --> 00:17:57,450
to kill my father.

263
00:17:58,770 --> 00:17:59,580
I also know

264
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:03,090
that you
were already pregnant at that time.

265
00:18:04,660 --> 00:18:06,770
You were no longer just my Shao Yang.

266
00:18:10,420 --> 00:18:11,290
Rest assured!

267
00:18:11,380 --> 00:18:12,710
Yuan Xiaoliu won't die!

268
00:18:17,490 --> 00:18:19,750
I have already swapped the poisoned tea.

269
00:18:20,100 --> 00:18:21,690
Actually, I knew that the Empress Dowager

270
00:18:21,690 --> 00:18:23,150
came to tonight's meeting

271
00:18:23,450 --> 00:18:24,530
in the name of love,

272
00:18:25,290 --> 00:18:27,610
but in truth, she came for your life.

273
00:18:28,260 --> 00:18:30,520
But Your Majesty, I also wanted you to see

274
00:18:31,330 --> 00:18:33,660
the lingering affection between you two.

275
00:18:33,820 --> 00:18:35,420
Yuan Xiaoliu could have left,

276
00:18:35,420 --> 00:18:37,480
but he wanted to see you one last time.

277
00:18:37,690 --> 00:18:38,550
There's no need

278
00:18:38,890 --> 00:18:40,920
for you two to fight to the death.

279
00:18:43,860 --> 00:18:45,250
I can spare your life,

280
00:18:46,260 --> 00:18:47,740
but I need a promise.

281
00:18:50,970 --> 00:18:52,210
As long as you live,

282
00:18:52,940 --> 00:18:55,700
you must never set foot in Northern Qin.

283
00:18:58,290 --> 00:18:59,050
I promise.

284
00:19:00,520 --> 00:19:01,720
I will give the order.

285
00:19:02,050 --> 00:19:05,450
Northern Qin won't send anyone
to hunt you down anymore.

286
00:19:06,340 --> 00:19:07,450
From now on,

287
00:19:08,690 --> 00:19:10,170
you can live freely.

288
00:19:17,250 --> 00:19:17,920
Watch out!

289
00:19:22,810 --> 00:19:23,330
Yaoyao!

290
00:19:25,530 --> 00:19:26,730
It's Mulian Yu's men.

291
00:19:27,180 --> 00:19:28,620
He wants me dead.

292
00:19:29,510 --> 00:19:30,770
If I die in Southern Ye,

293
00:19:31,820 --> 00:19:33,550
the peace talks will be ruined.

294
00:19:35,860 --> 00:19:36,490
Shao Yang!

295
00:19:40,770 --> 00:19:41,500
Come with me!

296
00:19:47,290 --> 00:19:48,690
Shao Yang, hang in there!

297
00:19:48,860 --> 00:19:50,260
I will get you out safely!

298
00:19:56,690 --> 00:19:58,620
Your Highness, we can continue.

299
00:20:01,420 --> 00:20:03,550
Your Highness, to achieve your goals,

300
00:20:03,940 --> 00:20:05,740
you really do whatever it takes.

301
00:20:07,620 --> 00:20:09,180
Princess Pingning is not only

302
00:20:09,180 --> 00:20:10,910
the sister of your best friend,

303
00:20:11,010 --> 00:20:13,870
but also like a sister
to your secondary concubine.

304
00:20:13,940 --> 00:20:16,140
Don't you have any mercy?

305
00:20:16,860 --> 00:20:19,660
You keep saying it's for the people
of Southern Ye,

306
00:20:19,660 --> 00:20:20,970
but it's just for your own

307
00:20:20,970 --> 00:20:22,380
lust for power and ambition.

308
00:20:22,380 --> 00:20:23,820
So what?

309
00:20:24,620 --> 00:20:25,820
For the Beifu Reform

310
00:20:25,970 --> 00:20:27,500
and to reclaim the Capital,

311
00:20:27,500 --> 00:20:28,830
I can sacrifice anyone.

312
00:20:29,860 --> 00:20:32,460
So, Your Highness,
you have no choice tonight.

313
00:20:32,710 --> 00:20:34,800
This pact must be signed.

314
00:20:35,770 --> 00:20:37,140
What if I don't?

315
00:20:40,580 --> 00:20:41,450
Bad news!

316
00:20:42,660 --> 00:20:45,060
There's been a murder at Xiyue Restaurant!

317
00:20:45,140 --> 00:20:46,380
It's just a place of entertainment.

318
00:20:46,380 --> 00:20:47,580
What's to panic about?

319
00:20:47,580 --> 00:20:50,440
The Empress Dowager of Northern Qin
was also there!

320
00:20:57,250 --> 00:20:58,380
Did you think

321
00:20:58,490 --> 00:21:01,020
I would only send people
to kill Yuan Xiaoliu?

322
00:21:01,490 --> 00:21:03,100
Having fought with you for years,

323
00:21:03,100 --> 00:21:05,430
I naturally knew you'd have a backup plan.

324
00:21:06,010 --> 00:21:08,740
So I had people
ambush outside Xiyue Restaurant.

325
00:21:09,210 --> 00:21:10,900
If Xie Jiayu really managed to resolve

326
00:21:10,900 --> 00:21:12,970
the grudge between Yuan Xiaoliu
and the Empress Dowager,

327
00:21:12,970 --> 00:21:15,690
then I might as well
kill the Empress Dowager too.

328
00:21:15,690 --> 00:21:19,100
If the dignified Empress Dowager
of Northern Qin dies in Southern Ye,

329
00:21:19,100 --> 00:21:21,180
what will the situation be?

330
00:21:23,580 --> 00:21:26,620
Since Southern Ye broke the alliance
and the marriage agreement first,

331
00:21:26,620 --> 00:21:29,350
then sent assassins
to kill our Empress Dowager,

332
00:21:29,450 --> 00:21:31,620
-and...
-Prince Qi has arrived!

333
00:21:55,970 --> 00:21:57,170
Qing Long and Yan Yue?

334
00:21:57,190 --> 00:21:58,080
It's Xiao Wuyi.

335
00:21:59,140 --> 00:21:59,940
He knew long ago

336
00:21:59,940 --> 00:22:02,580
that I brought Yuan Xiaoliu to see
the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin.

337
00:22:02,580 --> 00:22:03,210
Let's go!

338
00:22:21,500 --> 00:22:22,760
Eagle King, Mulian Yu,

339
00:22:22,860 --> 00:22:26,120
receive the decree of the Empress Dowager
of Northern Qin.

340
00:22:29,210 --> 00:22:31,540
Eagle King Mulian Yu, receive the decree!

341
00:22:35,950 --> 00:22:38,100
Since you entered Ye
holding the tally of Northern Qin,

342
00:22:38,100 --> 00:22:40,180
you should follow the etiquette
of the world.

343
00:22:40,180 --> 00:22:43,100
Canceling the marriage agreement
with Princess Pingning

344
00:22:43,100 --> 00:22:44,660
and restoring the peace agreement

345
00:22:44,660 --> 00:22:47,340
is an act that follows the will
of heaven and the people.

346
00:22:47,340 --> 00:22:48,940
You're ordered
to sign the peace agreement immediately

347
00:22:48,940 --> 00:22:51,100
and return
the three prefectures to Southern Ye.

348
00:22:51,100 --> 00:22:51,900
Thus decreed.

349
00:22:53,340 --> 00:22:53,930
No.

350
00:22:54,580 --> 00:22:56,730
Xiyue Restaurant
is in a sea of fire right now.

351
00:22:56,730 --> 00:22:57,420
Our Empress Dowager...

352
00:22:57,420 --> 00:22:59,020
Your Empress Dowager has now

353
00:22:59,100 --> 00:23:01,300
returned safely to Honglu Temple.

354
00:23:01,770 --> 00:23:03,230
And she asked me to tell you

355
00:23:03,250 --> 00:23:04,780
that she has long been aware

356
00:23:04,820 --> 00:23:06,340
of your actions tonight.

357
00:23:06,940 --> 00:23:07,770
Impossible.

358
00:23:08,010 --> 00:23:08,860
Impossible?

359
00:23:09,050 --> 00:23:11,690
You can ask Young Lord Xiao about this.

360
00:23:35,340 --> 00:23:36,010
Lejun.

361
00:23:37,660 --> 00:23:38,720
It's all right now.

362
00:23:43,420 --> 00:23:43,940
Wuyi.

363
00:23:44,420 --> 00:23:45,380
Although I said

364
00:23:45,490 --> 00:23:47,340
I couldn't hide behind you all the time,

365
00:23:47,340 --> 00:23:48,660
for what happened tonight,

366
00:23:48,660 --> 00:23:50,060
I still want to thank you.

367
00:23:50,770 --> 00:23:51,830
No need to thank me.

368
00:23:52,250 --> 00:23:53,780
You should thank Xie Jiayu.

369
00:23:54,580 --> 00:23:56,250
I originally wanted
to watch from the sidelines,

370
00:23:56,250 --> 00:23:58,140
but she didn't give up
time and time again.

371
00:23:58,140 --> 00:23:59,660
I couldn't help but admire her.

372
00:23:59,660 --> 00:24:01,720
So I placed spies in Xiyue Restaurant

373
00:24:01,860 --> 00:24:03,390
to ensure absolute safety.

374
00:24:05,580 --> 00:24:06,640
Where is Xie Jiayu?

375
00:24:08,820 --> 00:24:10,880
She was injured in Xiyue Restaurant.

376
00:24:18,660 --> 00:24:20,730
Your Highness, please wait.

377
00:24:25,290 --> 00:24:27,820
Your Highness,
are you going back on your word?

378
00:24:27,820 --> 00:24:29,860
The one who just promised
to cancel the political marriage

379
00:24:29,860 --> 00:24:31,260
is your Empress Dowager.

380
00:24:31,340 --> 00:24:33,180
I always keep my word

381
00:24:33,510 --> 00:24:34,770
and never go back on it.

382
00:24:35,660 --> 00:24:37,190
Then what do you want to say?

383
00:24:37,340 --> 00:24:38,600
On the day of the match,

384
00:24:38,630 --> 00:24:39,760
I took a fancy to you.

385
00:24:40,730 --> 00:24:42,860
Wanting to marry you
was my selfish desire,

386
00:24:42,860 --> 00:24:43,900
but not a pretense.

387
00:24:43,900 --> 00:24:46,420
Don't talk nonsense. Shut up.

388
00:24:46,490 --> 00:24:48,380
This is our custom in Northern Qin.

389
00:24:48,380 --> 00:24:49,510
If you want someone,

390
00:24:49,730 --> 00:24:50,860
you shout it out loud

391
00:24:51,010 --> 00:24:52,410
so that heaven will know.

392
00:24:52,420 --> 00:24:53,210
Li Lejun,

393
00:24:54,290 --> 00:24:55,420
with or without the political marriage,

394
00:24:55,420 --> 00:24:56,480
I want to marry you.

395
00:24:57,050 --> 00:24:58,250
If you are unwilling,

396
00:24:58,650 --> 00:24:59,650
I won't force you.

397
00:25:03,580 --> 00:25:05,490
If you change your mind one day,

398
00:25:05,660 --> 00:25:07,100
come to Northern Qin to find me.

399
00:25:07,100 --> 00:25:08,430
My Eagle King's Mansion

400
00:25:08,520 --> 00:25:10,450
will always open its doors for you!

401
00:25:51,770 --> 00:25:53,590
How is your injury?

402
00:25:56,140 --> 00:25:56,690
I'm fine.

403
00:25:57,290 --> 00:25:58,290
Ruisheng used

404
00:25:58,290 --> 00:25:59,450
the finest wound ointment on me.

405
00:25:59,450 --> 00:26:01,050
It won't leave a single scar.

406
00:26:10,450 --> 00:26:11,980
It seems to have succeeded.

407
00:26:21,140 --> 00:26:22,270
Thank you for today.

408
00:26:23,180 --> 00:26:23,970
Why thank me?

409
00:26:24,420 --> 00:26:26,780
You saved the life
of the Northern Qin Empress Dowager.

410
00:26:26,780 --> 00:26:28,420
If anything had happened to her
in Jiankang,

411
00:26:28,420 --> 00:26:29,940
the consequences
would have been unimaginable.

412
00:26:29,940 --> 00:26:31,400
Actually, I was just lucky

413
00:26:31,530 --> 00:26:32,390
and won the bet.

414
00:26:33,690 --> 00:26:35,750
But if you don't want to do something,

415
00:26:35,770 --> 00:26:37,100
no one can make you do it.

416
00:26:37,770 --> 00:26:39,660
You knew early on
that I took Yuan Xiaoliu,

417
00:26:39,660 --> 00:26:42,250
so you had Qing Long and Yan Yue
guard outside Xiyue Restaurant,

418
00:26:42,250 --> 00:26:43,050
didn't you?

419
00:26:45,100 --> 00:26:47,140
But if it weren't
for your repeated insistence,

420
00:26:47,140 --> 00:26:48,800
things wouldn't be like this.

421
00:26:49,210 --> 00:26:50,730
The Northern Qin Empress Dowager

422
00:26:50,730 --> 00:26:52,390
has agreed to the peace terms.

423
00:26:55,380 --> 00:26:57,340
Later, the Northern Qin Empress Dowager
told me

424
00:26:57,340 --> 00:26:58,450
that she didn't want
the Eagle King to gain the support

425
00:26:58,450 --> 00:27:00,620
of the Southern Ye royal family
in the first place.

426
00:27:00,620 --> 00:27:02,250
She just wanted to see Yuan Xiaoliu.

427
00:27:02,250 --> 00:27:03,980
That's why she made this trade.

428
00:27:04,530 --> 00:27:07,050
Do you think Yuan Xiaoliu and she

429
00:27:07,100 --> 00:27:08,630
really let go of each other?

430
00:27:12,660 --> 00:27:13,460
What's wrong?

431
00:27:14,380 --> 00:27:15,180
Yizhi...

432
00:27:18,100 --> 00:27:19,030
wants to see you.

433
00:27:24,730 --> 00:27:25,590
-Yaoyao.
-Mao.

434
00:27:26,820 --> 00:27:27,880
How's your injury?

435
00:27:28,180 --> 00:27:29,240
Does it hurt badly?

436
00:27:30,250 --> 00:27:32,110
I'm fine. It's just a flesh wound.

437
00:27:34,140 --> 00:27:36,820
Lejun's marriage agreement
has finally been canceled.

438
00:27:36,820 --> 00:27:37,860
You two siblings

439
00:27:38,340 --> 00:27:40,340
don't have to be separated anymore.

440
00:27:40,970 --> 00:27:42,530
When I leave Jiankang with you,

441
00:27:42,530 --> 00:27:44,460
I'll figure something out for her.

442
00:27:47,530 --> 00:27:48,240
Mao.

443
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:50,980
I know you won't leave.

444
00:27:53,180 --> 00:27:54,180
I also know

445
00:27:54,660 --> 00:27:57,190
you're about to marry a girl
of the Cui family.

446
00:27:57,210 --> 00:27:59,010
Although neither of you told me,

447
00:27:59,450 --> 00:28:00,860
I already knew

448
00:28:01,770 --> 00:28:03,570
when you went to the Cui Mansion.

449
00:28:04,250 --> 00:28:04,900
Yaoyao.

450
00:28:07,770 --> 00:28:08,570
Do you hate me?

451
00:28:10,420 --> 00:28:11,580
Why would I hate you?

452
00:28:14,250 --> 00:28:15,450
Sometimes I wonder

453
00:28:16,940 --> 00:28:19,200
if it's because I was too childish before

454
00:28:19,860 --> 00:28:21,730
that neither you nor Xiao Wuyi

455
00:28:22,050 --> 00:28:23,850
was willing to tell me the truth.

456
00:28:24,450 --> 00:28:25,900
I was a bit angry at first.

457
00:28:27,050 --> 00:28:28,450
You have such ambitions,

458
00:28:28,820 --> 00:28:30,550
but why didn't you ever tell me?

459
00:28:33,820 --> 00:28:34,950
But later I thought,

460
00:28:36,250 --> 00:28:38,290
it was always me wanting to do something

461
00:28:38,290 --> 00:28:40,150
and dragging you to accompany me.

462
00:28:42,100 --> 00:28:43,970
But I didn't know what you wanted.

463
00:28:44,900 --> 00:28:45,580
Actually,

464
00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:49,140
I never truly understood you.

465
00:28:49,940 --> 00:28:51,000
It's not like that.

466
00:28:52,010 --> 00:28:53,610
I just wanted to protect you.

467
00:28:53,940 --> 00:28:54,940
I hope you will live easily and happily

468
00:28:54,940 --> 00:28:56,290
for your whole life,

469
00:28:56,530 --> 00:28:57,690
and never see this world's

470
00:28:57,690 --> 00:28:58,660
cruel side.

471
00:29:02,290 --> 00:29:02,900
Yaoyao.

472
00:29:06,530 --> 00:29:08,380
Are you willing to enter the palace?

473
00:29:08,380 --> 00:29:09,530
Are you asking me to be your consort?

474
00:29:09,530 --> 00:29:10,660
I mean in the future.

475
00:29:11,530 --> 00:29:12,250
One day,

476
00:29:12,420 --> 00:29:13,750
I will truly hold power.

477
00:29:13,860 --> 00:29:15,010
At that time, there will be no He family

478
00:29:15,010 --> 00:29:15,770
or Cui family.

479
00:29:15,770 --> 00:29:16,970
There will only be us.

480
00:29:18,340 --> 00:29:18,970
I think

481
00:29:19,770 --> 00:29:21,570
you can divorce Xiao Wuyi first.

482
00:29:22,180 --> 00:29:23,970
Do you know there is
a Bureau of Devices in the palace?

483
00:29:23,970 --> 00:29:25,530
You can be a female official there.

484
00:29:25,530 --> 00:29:27,180
Don't you like mechanical devices?

485
00:29:27,180 --> 00:29:27,970
How could the craftsmanship
outside the palace

486
00:29:27,970 --> 00:29:29,370
be as good as that inside?

487
00:29:29,450 --> 00:29:30,580
But I don't like it.

488
00:29:39,470 --> 00:29:40,190
Mao.

489
00:29:41,690 --> 00:29:43,550
This is not the path I want to take.

490
00:29:45,940 --> 00:29:47,050
I have grown up.

491
00:29:48,820 --> 00:29:51,760
Between cruel truths and false illusions,

492
00:29:52,490 --> 00:29:53,490
I want the former.

493
00:29:56,490 --> 00:29:57,490
You just chose

494
00:29:58,250 --> 00:30:00,310
what you thought was more important.

495
00:30:00,320 --> 00:30:02,120
So you don't need to feel guilty,

496
00:30:02,530 --> 00:30:04,330
nor do you need to worry about me.

497
00:30:14,690 --> 00:30:16,150
So you still want to leave?

498
00:30:19,730 --> 00:30:21,210
But you have never left Jiankang,

499
00:30:21,210 --> 00:30:22,420
and you will be all alone...

500
00:30:22,420 --> 00:30:23,950
The road is beneath my feet.

501
00:30:24,450 --> 00:30:25,650
Only by traveling far

502
00:30:26,490 --> 00:30:28,820
will I know where my home is.

503
00:30:42,420 --> 00:30:43,750
It seems that right now,

504
00:30:45,900 --> 00:30:47,430
I still can't keep you here.

505
00:31:09,250 --> 00:31:10,510
You should be grateful

506
00:31:11,010 --> 00:31:12,070
that you survived.

507
00:31:12,940 --> 00:31:14,400
Phoenix Bone Poison Pill.

508
00:31:16,800 --> 00:31:20,000
Actually, today, it wasn't just her
who wanted to kill me;

509
00:31:21,050 --> 00:31:22,450
I also wanted to kill her.

510
00:31:22,810 --> 00:31:24,270
It was Jiayu's appearance

511
00:31:27,140 --> 00:31:28,540
that finally stopped me.

512
00:31:32,730 --> 00:31:33,730
What a waste.

513
00:31:37,530 --> 00:31:38,730
This girl Jiayu

514
00:31:39,860 --> 00:31:42,420
is always so drawn to the light

515
00:31:44,340 --> 00:31:45,530
and so passionate that the dark

516
00:31:45,530 --> 00:31:46,940
in one's heart

517
00:31:47,010 --> 00:31:48,140
has nowhere to hide.

518
00:31:49,530 --> 00:31:52,330
It makes me reluctant
to be too cruel to this world.

519
00:32:00,100 --> 00:32:01,530
Is this also the reason

520
00:32:02,290 --> 00:32:03,490
why you fell for her?

521
00:32:12,210 --> 00:32:14,470
The last time I saw you drinking like this

522
00:32:15,100 --> 00:32:16,580
was at Jiuzhang Plain,

523
00:32:17,340 --> 00:32:18,740
when there was no way out.

524
00:32:27,010 --> 00:32:28,540
Now that she's not leaving,

525
00:32:28,940 --> 00:32:31,010
is it possible for the two of you to...

526
00:32:31,010 --> 00:32:32,540
I don't have much time left.

527
00:32:34,530 --> 00:32:35,450
Xie Jiayu...

528
00:32:38,050 --> 00:32:40,250
Xie Jiayu was never my responsibility.

529
00:32:40,620 --> 00:32:42,550
And I have never expected her to be.

530
00:32:43,690 --> 00:32:44,890
I promised her mother

531
00:32:45,770 --> 00:32:47,370
not to involve her in danger.

532
00:32:49,100 --> 00:32:50,450
Haven't I told you?

533
00:32:51,450 --> 00:32:52,940
I read the fortune for you two.

534
00:32:52,940 --> 00:32:55,380
Your destiny with her
definitely won't just end here.

535
00:32:55,380 --> 00:32:56,290
You two are...

536
00:32:56,290 --> 00:32:57,890
I never believed in destiny.

537
00:32:59,620 --> 00:33:00,490
If what destiny leaves for me

538
00:33:00,490 --> 00:33:02,050
never belonged to me in the first place,

539
00:33:02,050 --> 00:33:03,250
I will personally...

540
00:33:03,340 --> 00:33:04,140
What?

541
00:33:09,010 --> 00:33:09,860
Cut it off.

542
00:33:15,690 --> 00:33:16,490
Cut it off?

543
00:33:37,380 --> 00:33:38,110
You're back?

544
00:33:40,050 --> 00:33:41,780
Why haven't you gone to bed yet?

545
00:33:42,210 --> 00:33:42,900
Tonight...

546
00:33:46,440 --> 00:33:48,170
the moonlight is quite pretty.

547
00:33:56,530 --> 00:33:57,530
Have you...

548
00:33:58,940 --> 00:34:00,340
talked it out with Yizhi?

549
00:34:06,140 --> 00:34:07,800
Maybe ordinary people like us

550
00:34:08,050 --> 00:34:09,790
and people with lofty ambitions like you

551
00:34:09,790 --> 00:34:11,920
were never meant to walk the same path.

552
00:34:23,780 --> 00:34:25,310
Not having great ambitions

553
00:34:26,050 --> 00:34:27,909
doesn't mean having no backbone.

554
00:34:28,780 --> 00:34:29,380
Xie Jiayu,

555
00:34:31,820 --> 00:34:33,280
you're a very good person.

556
00:34:41,090 --> 00:34:43,750
I have decided
to take Yuan Xiaoliu as my master.

557
00:34:43,949 --> 00:34:44,840
From now on,

558
00:34:44,860 --> 00:34:47,699
I will follow him to improve my skills
in mechanics and construction.

559
00:34:47,699 --> 00:34:48,960
I will leave Jiankang.

560
00:34:49,530 --> 00:34:51,969
Maybe I will follow him to your Beifu.

561
00:34:57,010 --> 00:34:57,780
Xiao Wuyi.

562
00:34:58,050 --> 00:34:59,010
Yuan Xiaoliu's Cangfeng Forge

563
00:34:59,010 --> 00:35:00,170
works really well for me.

564
00:35:00,170 --> 00:35:01,860
Can you ask him
to share half of it with me?

565
00:35:01,860 --> 00:35:04,700
Who told you that Cangfeng Forge
belongs to Yuan Xiaoliu?

566
00:35:04,700 --> 00:35:05,630
Whose is it then?

567
00:35:07,220 --> 00:35:07,900
It's mine.

568
00:35:08,530 --> 00:35:09,610
Then can you share half

569
00:35:09,610 --> 00:35:10,900
of your Cangfeng Forge with me?

570
00:35:10,900 --> 00:35:12,300
Anyway,
after you go to the Northern Border,

571
00:35:12,300 --> 00:35:13,700
you won't use it anymore.

572
00:35:15,700 --> 00:35:16,860
Let me think about it.

573
00:35:16,860 --> 00:35:18,320
You need to think about it?

574
00:35:22,970 --> 00:35:24,430
Why can't I think about it?

575
00:35:25,010 --> 00:35:26,050
Even if I'm not at home,

576
00:35:26,050 --> 00:35:27,380
this home is still mine.

577
00:35:28,050 --> 00:35:29,900
With such a petty personality,

578
00:35:29,970 --> 00:35:31,900
no wonder you can't find yourself a girl.

579
00:35:31,900 --> 00:35:33,700
I already have 3 concubines in my mansion,

580
00:35:33,700 --> 00:35:35,500
which is annoying enough for me.

581
00:35:36,380 --> 00:35:37,380
Do the three of us

582
00:35:37,380 --> 00:35:38,980
have anything to do with you?

583
00:35:39,410 --> 00:35:40,780
If you keep acting like this,

584
00:35:40,780 --> 00:35:42,240
you'll be single forever.

585
00:35:42,820 --> 00:35:44,010
In case you die in the future,

586
00:35:44,010 --> 00:35:45,260
no one will collect your body.

587
00:35:45,260 --> 00:35:46,340
Taking heaven and earth as one's grave

588
00:35:46,340 --> 00:35:47,670
is also a kind of beauty.

589
00:35:48,090 --> 00:35:49,350
I don't need a partner.

590
00:35:51,220 --> 00:35:53,420
And I definitely don't need a weakness.

591
00:35:55,380 --> 00:35:57,980
I don't believe
you don't have anyone you like.

592
00:36:01,570 --> 00:36:02,530
No, no, no.

593
00:36:02,700 --> 00:36:03,490
That look in your eyes—

594
00:36:03,490 --> 00:36:05,050
you definitely have someone you like.

595
00:36:05,050 --> 00:36:05,820
What does she look like?

596
00:36:05,820 --> 00:36:06,820
Tell me about her.

597
00:36:06,980 --> 00:36:08,710
What does it have to do with you?

598
00:36:09,050 --> 00:36:10,010
Just gossiping.

599
00:36:10,170 --> 00:36:13,770
It's precisely because it has
nothing to do with me that I can ask.

600
00:36:24,780 --> 00:36:26,180
Why are you staring at me?

601
00:36:28,450 --> 00:36:29,380
Anyway...

602
00:36:30,970 --> 00:36:32,300
she is prettier than you

603
00:36:32,610 --> 00:36:33,900
and more sensible than you.

604
00:36:33,900 --> 00:36:35,610
She's better than you in everything.

605
00:36:35,610 --> 00:36:36,420
Impossible.

606
00:36:36,940 --> 00:36:37,820
In this world,

607
00:36:37,820 --> 00:36:39,420
there can't be such a person.

608
00:36:46,820 --> 00:36:48,340
Didn't you write a divorce paper

609
00:36:48,340 --> 00:36:49,490
for Yuanji?

610
00:36:49,970 --> 00:36:51,340
Before you go to the Northern Border,

611
00:36:51,340 --> 00:36:52,650
write me one too, will you?

612
00:36:52,650 --> 00:36:54,420
Aren't you not in a hurry to leave?

613
00:36:54,420 --> 00:36:56,150
Why do you need a divorce paper?

614
00:36:56,300 --> 00:36:57,220
Stop pretending.

615
00:36:57,220 --> 00:36:58,090
I saw your discarded draft

616
00:36:58,090 --> 00:36:59,220
on the desk that day.

617
00:36:59,900 --> 00:37:01,570
Just be a good person to the end.

618
00:37:01,570 --> 00:37:03,230
Who told you I'm a good person?

619
00:37:04,490 --> 00:37:06,010
Didn't you say earlier

620
00:37:06,340 --> 00:37:08,300
that I would laugh at you
from the bottom of my heart?

621
00:37:08,300 --> 00:37:09,830
How could I be a good person?

622
00:37:31,490 --> 00:37:34,050
[Honglu Temple]

623
00:37:32,950 --> 00:37:33,780
Mulian Yu,

624
00:37:34,450 --> 00:37:36,250
you attempted to assassinate me

625
00:37:36,490 --> 00:37:38,170
and committed rebellion
against the throne.

626
00:37:38,170 --> 00:37:41,370
According to the law,
your nine clans should be executed!

627
00:37:48,090 --> 00:37:50,820
But I am willing
to spare you the death penalty,

628
00:37:51,560 --> 00:37:54,440
because you are
the right-hand man of Northern Qin.

629
00:37:55,530 --> 00:37:56,940
Our territory

630
00:37:57,610 --> 00:37:58,740
still needs

631
00:37:58,740 --> 00:38:01,450
a blood-stained sword like you
to guard it.

632
00:38:03,220 --> 00:38:05,750
Thank you, Your Majesty,
for sparing my life.

633
00:38:10,780 --> 00:38:12,340
Recorded in this roster

634
00:38:13,050 --> 00:38:16,310
are the unextinguished hidden forces
of our Northern Qin.

635
00:38:16,610 --> 00:38:18,820
Now I'm entrusting it to you.

636
00:38:20,400 --> 00:38:21,810
And Xie Huaigui.

637
00:38:23,050 --> 00:38:25,850
His obsession with avenging
the An and Lu families

638
00:38:26,380 --> 00:38:28,650
is the sharpest blade
for stirring up turmoil in Jiankang

639
00:38:28,650 --> 00:38:31,510
and hindering
Southern Ye's northern expedition.

640
00:38:32,780 --> 00:38:33,900
You should know

641
00:38:34,170 --> 00:38:35,220
how to use him.

642
00:38:35,380 --> 00:38:36,310
Your Majesty, I,

643
00:38:37,220 --> 00:38:39,050
with all due respect,
would like to ask one more thing.

644
00:38:39,050 --> 00:38:42,170
Regarding the case of the Right King of Virtue
conspiring with the enemy and committing treason,

645
00:38:42,170 --> 00:38:44,230
was the evidence truly irrefutable,

646
00:38:44,260 --> 00:38:46,520
or was it a grand miscarriage of justice?

647
00:38:53,970 --> 00:38:55,650
Of course it was a miscarriage of justice.

648
00:38:55,650 --> 00:38:57,090
Otherwise, why would Mulian Ying

649
00:38:57,090 --> 00:38:59,010
hate me to the core?

650
00:39:00,020 --> 00:39:01,810
It was me who personally presented

651
00:39:01,810 --> 00:39:04,770
this vicious scheme to the late Emperor.

652
00:39:06,900 --> 00:39:08,300
And it was me

653
00:39:10,340 --> 00:39:12,540
who wiped out the entire Mulian family.

654
00:39:32,160 --> 00:39:37,300
♪ The past is dust,
we're passing through ♪

655
00:39:38,230 --> 00:39:43,810
♪ No regrets for what we've lost and won ♪

656
00:39:44,470 --> 00:39:50,770
♪ The shape of time begins to fade ♪

657
00:39:51,040 --> 00:39:57,520
♪ Half by choice, half washed away ♪

658
00:39:58,030 --> 00:40:03,450
♪ If fate is fragile,
what is right or wrong ♪

659
00:40:04,050 --> 00:40:09,420
♪ We only live for what we can't let go ♪

660
00:40:10,220 --> 00:40:13,870
♪ Love and hate fade
like the shifting sand ♪

661
00:40:13,970 --> 00:40:16,420
♪ What's right or wrong is better
left unsaid ♪

662
00:40:16,650 --> 00:40:22,670
♪ Every soul is bound by cause and fate ♪

663
00:40:21,530 --> 00:40:22,940
Memorial on the Beifu Reform.

664
00:40:22,940 --> 00:40:26,500
♪ The past is gone, so let it slip away ♪

665
00:40:24,570 --> 00:40:26,520
After deliberation by the ministers
of the Commandant of Justice,

666
00:40:26,520 --> 00:40:29,490
♪ The heart's a cage,
but peace will break the chains ♪

667
00:40:27,090 --> 00:40:29,520
the Regent requests
His Majesty's review and approval.

668
00:40:29,520 --> 00:40:34,990
♪ No need to speak,
just leave it all to fate ♪

669
00:40:29,530 --> 00:40:31,650
The "Memorial on the Beifu Reform"
submitted by

670
00:40:31,650 --> 00:40:33,570
Xiao Wuyi,
the Grand General of Beifu, is excellent.

671
00:40:33,570 --> 00:40:34,940
It has received His Majesty's approval.

672
00:40:34,940 --> 00:40:37,900
Xiao Wuyi,
Grand General of Beifu, is appointed

673
00:40:37,970 --> 00:40:39,970
Commander-in-Chief of the Six Prefectures.

674
00:40:39,970 --> 00:40:41,940
He shall oversee all military
and administrative affairs of Beifu

675
00:40:41,940 --> 00:40:43,870
under the authority of the Regent.

676
00:40:44,170 --> 00:40:46,490
He shall urge the various prefectures
to provide troops, horses,

677
00:40:46,490 --> 00:40:48,300
provisions, and supplies without delay,

678
00:40:48,300 --> 00:40:49,570
with all matters to be coordinated
under one command.

679
00:40:49,260 --> 00:40:54,680
♪ If fate is fragile,
what is right or wrong ♪

680
00:40:50,420 --> 00:40:54,380
Xiao Wuyi shall immediately lead his troops
back to the Northern Border.

681
00:40:54,380 --> 00:40:56,650
Xiao Yao is appointed
Director of Waterways

682
00:40:55,280 --> 00:41:00,650
♪ We only live for what we can't let go ♪

683
00:40:56,940 --> 00:41:00,300
and shall oversee all matters concerning the repair
of military supply routes and provisions.

684
00:41:00,300 --> 00:41:01,820
Thus decreed.

685
00:41:01,450 --> 00:41:05,100
♪ Love and hate fade
like the shifting sand ♪

686
00:41:02,050 --> 00:41:04,170
Thank you, Your Highness.

687
00:41:05,200 --> 00:41:07,650
♪ What's right or wrong is better
left unsaid ♪

688
00:41:07,850 --> 00:41:13,870
♪ Every soul is bound by cause and fate ♪

